version_description:
•A fresh look and more user-friendly experience.

•Simple to use for one-off tracking, without registering your details.

•Answers to your parcel queries with our brand new Frequently Asked Questions section.

•Start your parcel booki

Minor bug fixes
Fixed issue where users could not copy and paste tracking IDs

See parcel details displayed automatically (no need to enter a tracking number) when you register your delivery details on the App.

Previous tracking searches will also be ‘remembered’ and shown in a drop down box.
